                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p>This is a collection of long-form explanations of common idea and writing pitfalls that are often addressed in the <a href="/forum/c-89000">Ideas Critique</a> and <a href="/forum/c-50864">Drafts Critique</a> forums.</p>
<p><strong>As with my <a href="/mackenzie-tips">Writing Tips page</a>, these are all subjective observations and do not represent absolute truths or requirements.</strong> You are free to follow or ignore any of the items outlined here.</p>
